# Performance: Caching, Named Inputs & Bundling

Enable Nx local+remote cache, incremental typechecking, code-splitting, and lazy loading for heavy routes/assets.

**Justification:** Shortens feedback cycles and delivers faster user experiences on constrained devices.

## Nx Caching & Named Inputs

```json
{
  "namedInputs": {
    "default": [
      "{projectRoot}/**/*",
      "{workspaceRoot}/tsconfig.base.json",
      "!**/*.md"
    ]
  }
}
```

## Bundling & Splitting

- Tree-shake and split vendor/runtime chunks
- Lazy load admin/analytics routes
- Defer non-critical work with requestIdleCallback

